"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"There are ongoing attacks in Iran, Lebanon, and the surrounding region. In Israel, a refinery caught fire due to debris from a missile that was intercepted. This situation is happening after Spain decided not to allow the US to use two military bases in Andalusia that they run together.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ongoing Attacks in Middle East\",            \"translated_version\": \"Hay ataques en Ir\u00e1n, L\u00edbano y la regi\u00f3n cercana. En Israel, una refiner\u00eda se incendi\u00f3 por restos de un misil interceptado. Esto pasa despu\u00e9s de que Espa\u00f1a decidi\u00f3 no dejar que Estados Unidos use dos bases militares en Andaluc\u00eda que manejan juntos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques en Medio Oriente\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The eSafety regulator is worried about how social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, TikTok, and YouTube are following the rules about a ban.\",            \"english_title\": \"eSafety Concerns on Social Media\",            \"translated_version\": \"El regulador de seguridad electr\u00f3nica est\u00e1 preocupado por c\u00f3mo plataformas de redes sociales como Facebook, Instagram, Snapchat, TikTok y YouTube siguen las reglas sobre una prohibici\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Preocupaci\u00f3n de Seguridad en Redes Sociales\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A tanker has arrived in Cuban waters shortly after Donald Trump said he was okay with it. Meanwhile, Ukraine's president mentioned that partners are asking if the attacks can be reduced because prices are going up due to the war in Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tanker in Cuban Waters\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un barco lleg\u00f3 a aguas cubanas poco despu\u00e9s de que Donald Trump dijo que estaba de acuerdo. Mientras tanto, el presidente de Ucrania mencion\u00f3 que socios preguntan si los ataques pueden reducirse porque los precios est\u00e1n subiendo por la guerra en Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Barco en Aguas Cubanas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A new law was passed on Monday, which was strongly supported by the far-right and Security Minister Itamar Ben-Gvir. This law is happening while at least eight children, who were premature newborns, were evacuated during heavy fighting in Gaza at the start of the war.\",            \"english_title\": \"New Law and Gaza Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una nueva ley fue aprobada el lunes, apoyada por la extrema derecha y el Ministro de Seguridad Itamar Ben-Gvir. Esta ley ocurre mientras al menos ocho ni\u00f1os, que eran reci\u00e9n nacidos prematuros, fueron evacuados durante fuertes combates en Gaza al inicio de la guerra.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Nueva Ley y Conflicto en Gaza\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Merz's government is being stricter on refugees and migrants because more people are supporting the anti-immigration AfD party. This comes after a second fatal incident in the last 24 hours, according to Unifil, following Israel's expansion of its operation against Hezbollah.\",            \"english_title\": \"Stricter Policies on Refugees\",            \"translated_version\": \"El gobierno de Merz est\u00e1 siendo m\u00e1s estricto con refugiados y migrantes porque m\u00e1s personas apoyan al partido anti-inmigraci\u00f3n AfD. Esto pasa despu\u00e9s de un segundo incidente fatal en las \u00faltimas 24 horas, seg\u00fan Unifil, tras la expansi\u00f3n de la operaci\u00f3n de Israel contra Hezbollah.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pol\u00edticas M\u00e1s Estrictas para Refugiados\"        }    ]}"